00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:03,629
&gt;&gt; Lindera benzoin or spicebush.

2
00:00:03,629 --> 00:00:08,339
This is a beautiful shrub for the understory in the woodlands.

3
00:00:08,339 --> 00:00:12,179
It has beautiful, golden-yellow fall color.

4
00:00:12,179 --> 00:00:15,105
When you crush the leaves it has a spicy scent,

5
00:00:15,105 --> 00:00:17,219
hence the name spicebush.

6
00:00:17,219 --> 00:00:21,269
Distinctive feature is greenish twigs with clusters of

7
00:00:21,269 --> 00:00:26,774
very small flower buds at the nodes or the axils of the branches.

8
00:00:26,774 --> 00:00:30,820
This is Lindera benzoin, spicebush.

